{"tid":1920020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 年其實除左有東京奧運之外，仲有杜拜世博","createTime":"2020-03-11T07:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T08:23:46.000Z","uid":256077,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7201d8f584299f39fb5e211af4b7e4cbc2c882","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"呢排小弟睇過呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n杜拜係咪呢排多左人去，見無線都介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893144</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照計呢啲比較冷門既旅遊地方<br />\n唔知點解CCTVB 不停咁 Sell 佢<br />\n<br />\n後來搵下搵下先知今年除咗有東京奧運<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係仲有杜拜世博<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n杜拜世博應該係十月尾就會開幕<br />\nUAE 宜家有最新應該有74 個確診武肺<br />\n應該個政府都好撚驚同東京奧運同一命運<br />\n成個Project 已經駛咗 AED 33 billion<br />\n大概係 HKD 700 億<br />\n加上宜家油價不停咁跌<br />\n油王國啲經濟都麻麻地<br />\n如果個世博要取消既話實玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟幾年前去過杜拜<br />\n佢哋已經係不停咁起野去迎接個世博<br />\n最出名既就係<br />\n全世界最高大廈 Dubai Creek Tower<br />\n全世界最大摩天輪 Dubai Eyes<br />\n個政府已經駛左好多錢係旅遊到<br />\n（可能都有俾錢CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n至於宜家既狀況係點可以睇吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.arabianbusiness.com/politics-economics/442227-expo-2020-dubai-plans-on-track-despite-coronavirus-threat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabianbusiness.com%2Fpolitics-economics%2F442227-expo-2020-dubai-plans-on-track-despite-coronavirus-threat&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=d71dc9f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.arabianbusiness.com/politics-economics/442227-expo-2020-dubai-plans-on-track-despite-coronavirus-threat</a><br />\n<br />\n大概同日本政府差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係同 International Bureau of Exposition 傾緊<br />\n睇吓駛唔駛取消<br />\n<br />\n至於大家最想知既UAE 政府奶唔奶共<br />\n下面一幅圖講哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/fHftxyYnvPAkeT4b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FfHftxyYnvPAkeT4b8&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=bafbcd4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://images.app.goo.gl/fHftxyYnvPAkeT4b8</a>"},{"pid":"1644bb4b599040f103e34101a07bb10cf35dad33","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"669468951c923e3e640059455b914fff0a760df4","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"03cc5775589af1c6d2cec18dfe7892a6bbeaedf9","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c605bb2607c43e64d86ea76568d9427380561758","tid":1920020,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=55