後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec2a6985304b85a03111facd205b554caf1c48c","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2baf72dee747b19b26d2ad6a1686fe6eeb599c78","tid":1920020,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"杜拜冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"對比日本韓國歐洲泰國來講算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部分應該都係轉機客<br />\n係杜拜玩兩三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40250d0b39a13bac07a4c1a95555a76213cdcb40","tid":1920020,"uid":124473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"最快應該係歐洲國家盃...."},{"pid":"b71fcddc964688628c8df47ff559bb12b3221ac6","tid":1920020,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:58:13.000Z","msg":"油王國會怕蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2402859186cb7a577311bd2872245375d80224b","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2589f0919d0aeb53cc876419b628c6b6870b8fb4","tid":1920020,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"中東佬大把錢 who fucking care?<br />\n另外巴打話杜拜冷門我當堂嚇一跳 然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"宜家隔離post先話油價開始跌<br />\n其實杜拜係無乜石油<br />\n要靠大佬阿布扎比來幫佢<br />\n宜家油價開始跌<br />\n可能阿布扎比都難啲救到佢<br />\n<br />\nBtw 杜拜其實都好多香港人去<br />\n但係對比其他好熱門既地方<br />\n佢算少啲人去<br />\n照計CCTVB都係sell 星馬 日本 泰國 台灣 韓國<br />\n平時好少sell 杜拜<br />\n宜家 sell 到係幾個節目都一齊係到sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945a0657a0e31e429b490ec4e9f8eafc950d02cb","tid":1920020,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71fcddc964688628c8df47ff559bb12b3221ac6","tid":1920020,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:58:13.000Z","msg":"油王國會怕蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"杜拜試過金融危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ec5e29362207f1b7d31132e484881114403aac","tid":1920020,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜拜世博應該係十月尾就會開幕<br />\nUAE 宜家有最新應該有74 個確診武肺<br />\n應該個政府都好撚驚同東京奧運同一命運<br />\n成個Project 已經駛咗 AED 33 billion<br />\n大概係 HKD 700 億<br />\n加上宜家油價不停咁跌<br />\n油王國啲經濟都麻麻地<br />\n如果個世博要取消既話實玩完#</blockquote><br />\n石油產業佔UAE嘅GDP大約3成 佔杜拜得1-2%左右 <br />\n雖然無石油收入杜拜都唔會死 但無遊客到訪就肯定死撚梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816cd9a1e0f562c93619f772e68915ed26dc2f66","tid":1920020,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZGfUkBaRjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhZGfUkBaRjA&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6